<section class="py-5 mt-5">
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Getting Started</h1>
    <p class="lead">Set up and run the Phase 1 terrestrial DTN network with amateur radio hardware.</p>

    <h2 class="mt-4">Prerequisites</h2>
    <p>You will need the following hardware, software, and licensing:</p>
    <ul class="list-group list-group-flush mb-4">
      {{#each content.prerequisites}}
      <li class="list-group-item">{{this}}</li>
      {{/each}}
    </ul>

    <h2 class="mt-4">Installation</h2>
    <p>Clone the repository and build the HDTN software and DTN node binary:</p>
    {{#each content.installation}}
    {{> code-block language="bash" code=this}}
    {{/each}}

    <h2 class="mt-4">Run the Network</h2>
    <p>Start two DTN nodes to form a terrestrial network:</p>
    {{#each content.runNetwork}}
    {{> code-block language="bash" code=this}}
    {{/each}}

    <h2 class="mt-4">Test Connectivity</h2>
    <p>Verify the network is operational by sending a ping and a file:</p>
    {{#each content.testConnectivity}}
    {{> code-block language="bash" code=this}}
    {{/each}}

    <div class="alert alert-info mt-4" role="alert">
      <h3 class="h6">Note</h3>
      <p class="mb-0">An amateur radio license is required for over-the-air transmission. Ensure your callsign is configured in the AX.25 framing before transmitting.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
